    <p>Point your IPTV app at one of, some apps only accept the .m3u or .m3u8 extensions:
        <code class="code-block">{{ iptv_main_url }}</code>
        <code class="code-block">{{ iptv_main_url }}.m3u</code>
        <code class="code-block">{{ iptv_main_url }}.m3u8</code>
        The channel list will only provide
        entries with a quality greater than zero.
    </p>
    <p>Some apps will only work if this site is on https.</p>
    <h3>Recommended Apps</h3>
    <p>Many apps are made to be players for their subscription IPTV services, and on the side offer loading external
        playlists. These recommendations are tested, free and don't nag you to pay. Also check out this list <a
            href="https://awesomelists.top/#/iptv-org/awesome-iptv">Awesome IPTV</a>.</p>
    <p>The apps featured here have been tested to work.</p>
